moduli (tabled6.dat), and closure phases (tabled7.dat). The{\textasciitilde}description
of the reductions is given in Appendices A (the spectroscopy), B (the
photometry), and C (the spectro-interferometry). The procedure of
radial-velocity measuring is described in Sect. 3.1. Headers of Tables
D.1-D.7 published electronically are also given in Appendix D.

(7 data files).},
