target for precise radial velocity measurements. K2-136A c is the first
Neptune-sized planet to be found orbiting in a binary system within an
open cluster. The Hyades is the nearest star cluster to the Sun, has an
age of 625-750 Myr, and forms one of the fundamental rungs in the
