	abstract = {We describe how terrestrial planets in the habitable zones of Sun-like stars (i.e. FGK dwarfs) offer the best chance of discovering planets with conditions and evolutionary histories analogous to Earth's, as well as the best opportunity to detect unambiguous biosignatures.},
